            },
            "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000016"
          },
          {
            "type": "faq",
            "value": {
              "items": [
                {
                  "question": "What is OpenStax?",
                  "id": "what-is-openstax",
                  "answer": "<p data-block-key=\"a1\">OpenStax is a nonprofit educational initiative based at Rice University. We publish free, peer-reviewed, openly licensed textbooks and learning tools used by millions of students worldwide.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "question": "Are OpenStax textbooks really free?",
                  "id": "are-books-free",
                  "answer": "<p data-block-key=\"a2\">Yes. Every OpenStax textbook is free to read online and free to download as a PDF. If you would like a print copy, you can order one at a low cost that covers printing and shipping.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "question": "How do I adopt an OpenStax book for my course?",
                  "id": "how-to-adopt",
                  "answer": "<p data-block-key=\"a3\">Browse our subjects, find a book that fits your course, and let us know you are using it. Adopting takes only a few minutes and unlocks instructor resources.</p><ul><li data-block-key=\"a3a\">Choose your book</li><li data-block-key=\"a3b\">Tell us you are using it</li><li data-block-key=\"a3c\">Access test banks, slides, and more</li></ul>"
                }
              ],
              "config": []
            },
            "id": "c8a3f1e2-2222-0000-0000-000000000001"
          },
          {
            "type": "section",
            "value": {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "<h3 data-block-key=\"faqe2\">Multiple answers open, custom accent color, H2 headings</h3>",
                  "id": "c8a3f1e2-1111-0000-0000-000000000017"
                }
              ],
              "config": [
                {
